# ---------- Data caches ----------
# yfinance OHLCV + derived field parquets — regenerated on first request.
# Tracking them produces 80+ "modified" entries every 24h cache refresh and
# bloats the repo with binary churn. Use a persistent disk / Docker volume
# in production to avoid the cold-start re-download penalty.
backend/data/cache/
